summary:
I’m an enthusiastic, self-motivated UX/UI and Graphic Designer from Argentina, currently living at Amsterdam.
I’m enterprising and creative when it comes to new projects and I enjoy collaborating with colleagues and clients, developing and applying powerful and innovative ideas.
My passion about continuous development led me to study UX/UI Design.
I strongly believe that good designs are user-focused and friendly. Nevertheless, as a Graphic Designer, I think that visual design can highly improve the user experience.
